# Product Identity

This project is an AI Native Dashboard Agent Platform.

It is NOT a traditional BI system.

The product principle:

Everything is generated.
Everything is an Artifact.


# Core Workflow

All dashboard generation must follow:

User Intent

↓

Intent Understanding

↓

Dataset Understanding

↓

Dashboard Planning

↓

Design Application

↓

Artifact Generation

↓

Quality Review


Never directly:

User Request → LLM → HTML


# Architecture Rules

Frontend only handles:

- User interaction
- File upload
- Chat UI
- Preview


Business logic must live in:

agents/

services/

skills/

prompts/


Do not put AI workflow logic inside React components.


# Forbidden Product Direction

Do NOT implement:

- Drag and drop dashboard builder
- Widget editor
- Chart configuration UI
- Dashboard designer
- SQL builder
- Traditional BI modeling


# Deployment Principle

The product must run independently after deployment.

Cursor is only a development tool.

Do not rely on Cursor runtime.


# AI Rules

LLM calls must happen in backend.

Never expose API keys to frontend.

Use service abstraction for model providers.


# Dashboard Rules

Generated dashboards must follow:

- Apple inspired style
- Minimal
- Professional
- Responsive
- Mobile first
- KPI first
- 24px spacing
- 16px cards
- Maximum 5 colors
- No gradient background
- No 3D charts